FBIS3-39529 "drweu033_l_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 SPAIN Government Denies Entry Visa for Zhirinovskiy LD1602194694 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1900 GMT 16 Feb 94 LD1602194694 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Spanish Government has prohibited the entry into our country of Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, the ultranationalist leader and winner of the last Russian legislative elections, who was going to take part in a television program. According to sources at the Diplomatic Information Office, he has been refused an entry visa because his presence in Spain is not considered appropriate, a measure which had already been adopted by other European countries.
